---
import { SITE } from "@consts";
---

<section
  class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-1 items-center container mx-auto min-h-screen p-6 md:gap-16 gap-8 pt-18"
>
  <h1 class="heading text-[clamp(4rem,20vw,8.5rem)] uppercase">
    You don't need the next AI trick, you need correctness.
  </h1>
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <p class="text-4xl text-secondary">
      It looks like finding a professional with truly full-stack experience,
      from <b>computer science fundamentals</b>, to <b>sales engineering</b> is extremely
      hard nowadays. Add in the need for 
      <b>platform engineering, DevEx, AI knowledge, fault-tolerant design, high-throughput
        systems, and maintainability-first mindset,</b
      > and you might be feeling like asking for <b>the impossible.</b>
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center md:flex-row gap-2.5">
      <a
        class="w-full text-2xl sm:w-auto flex items-center justify-center bg-foreground text-background rounded-2xl py-3 px-6 sm:py-4 sm:px-10 cursor-pointer hover:bg-background hover:outline hover:outline-1 hover:outline-dashed hover:outline-secondary hover:text-foreground transition"
        href="#Contact">Let's Talk!</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
